public class SMBDeduplicationScenario
extends AbstractSMBScenario

Tests the new Remote Data Deduplication feature of Windows 2012 using SMB. (NOT IMPLEMENTED) This feature broke PHP in php bug #63241. This scenario will catch that or any other problems Deduplication causes to PHP. You can check if a file is deduplicated (on Windows) by running `fsutil reparsepoint query [file]`

Author:
Matt Ficken
